description.narrative: The Activity follows Pacific Maritime Safety Programme (PMSP) Phase 1 (2011-2015), and responds to the maritime safety issues through the following five broad components: Maritime safety awareness raising and engagement; Maritime sector regulatory framework; Maritime sector training; Vessel and navigational safety improvements; and Environmental and Search & Rescue.
